com.snamp.connectors

Class AttributePrimitiveTypeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snamp.connectors.AttributeTypeInfoBuilder
      • com.snamp.connectors.AttributePrimitiveTypeBuilder

  • public class AttributePrimitiveTypeBuilder
extends AttributeTypeInfoBuilder
    Represents builder for primitive types.

    This type system provides the following MIB-free data types that can be used to represent attribute values in your SNAMP connector:

    • Int8 - wrapper for Byte class.
    • Int16 - wrapper for Short class.
    • Int32 - wrapper for Integer class.
    • Int64 - wrapper for Long class.
    • String - wrapper for String class.
    • Integer - wrapper for BigInteger class.
    • Decimal - wrapper for BigDecimal class.
    • Boolean - wrapper for Boolean class.
    • Date - wrapper for Date and Calendar classes both.

    It is recommended to use this class as a base class for building your own MIB-specific type system.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Roman Sakno
